            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">3.904</ph> Procedures for filing complaints.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d152e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d154e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Any employee of a contractor who believes that he or she has been discharged, demoted, or otherwise discriminated against contrary to the policy in <xref href="FAR-id1617MD00H39.dita#id1617MD00H39"
                        base="i1123680"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">3.903</xref> may file a complaint with the Inspector General of the agency that awarded the contract.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d154e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            The complaint shall be signed and shall contain-</p>
					          <ol id="d152e35" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d154e39" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The name of the contractor;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d154e48" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The contract number, if known; if not, a description reasonably sufficient to identify the contract(s) involved;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d154e57" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The substantial violation of law giving rise to the disclosure;</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d154e66" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The nature of the disclosure giving rise to the discriminatory act; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d154e75" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(5)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The specific nature and date of the reprisal.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
		    </conbody>
